title: SET_BLIP_SPRITE
content:
0x8DBBB0B9// SetBlipSprite
void SET_BLIP_SPRITE(Blip blip, int spriteId);Parameters:blip: The blip to change.spriteId: The sprite ID to set.Sets the displayed sprite for a specific blip.
There's a list of sprites on the FiveM documentation site.This is the server-side RPC native equivalent of the client native SET_BLIP_SPRITE.
